Filter: Interspire
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version: 1.00
Author: Brendan Abbott <brendan@bloodbone.ws>
Build Date: 25 August 2009
Requirements: Symphony 2.0.6


Installation
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Enable the extension 'Filter: Interspire Email Marketer'

2. Go to the preferences tab and enter in your Interspire details

3. Add the filter to any events you need

4. Woohoo!


Notes
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The custom field relies on the FieldID value from within the Interspire interface,
not the name of the field.

The majority of this extension was a patch job of Rowan's Create + Send Filter, so
a cheerio to him :)
